-- Onex to sell The Warranty Group to TPG Capital
-- 
-- Fri Mar 21, 2014 08:20AM EDT
-- None



March 21 (Reuters) - Canadian private equity investment firm Onex Corp <OCX.TO> said it would sell The Warranty Group, a provider of extended warranty contracts, to an affiliate of TPG Capital Management LP[TPG.UL] for an enterprise value of about $1.5 billion.

The deal value includes earnings the business generates from Dec. 31, 2013 until the expected closing of the deal in the third quarter of the year. [ID:nCCN7Z1zYN]